1.title: Go! f
1.plot: The girls of f(x) head to Austin, Texas to attend the biggest music festival in America, SXSW. Join Victoria, Amber, Sulli, Luna and Krystal as they take over Austin. Then it's time to go back to the basics. They head to Los Angeles to get ready for their long awaited comeback. They also get to spend some quality time with their friends and loved ones.

2.title: Go! U-KISS
2.plot: The boys of U-KISS head to NYC, SF, and LA for their first ever U.S. Tour. Join the boys on tour as they take over the US. They also get to spend some quality time with their friends and loved ones. Check out the amazing time that the boys spent in the US.

3.title: Go! CNBLUE
3.plot: CNBLUE has finally landed in the states for their Blue Moon World Tour. Join in the journey with Mnet America as we follow the boys during their stay in the U.S. and Mexico.

4.title: Go! Teen Top
4.plot: Mnet America proudly presents Go! TEEN TOP as part of our exclusive Headliner Series. Mnet America brings you backstage footage from TEEN TOP's "High Kick" tour in cities like NY, CA, and San Jose as well as an exclusive behind the scenes glimpse into their photo shoots, interviews and much, much more! This never-before-seen story will show the amazing tour that Niel, Chunji, Changjo, C.A.P, L. Joe and Ricky have spent in the U.S!

5.title: Go! B.A.P
5.plot: Mnet America proudly presents Go! B.A.P as part of our exclusive Headliner Series. The boys of B.A.P go on a romantic adventure at Central Park, New York, then continue their date at the Santa Monica Promenade where Zelo shows off his beat boxing skills and test rides his custom made skateboard! Check out exclusive backstage footage from B.A.P's "Live on Earth 2014" tour as well as their personal messages to their fans during their final night at the Griffith Observatory. This never-before-seen story will show the amazing tour that Yongguk, Himchan, Daehyun, Jongup, ...

6.title: Go! B1A4
6.plot: Mnet America proudly presents Go! B1A4 as part of our exclusive Headliner Series! Watch as B1A4 visit sunny LA for the very first time to perform at the 2014 Korea Times Music Festival! We bring you exclusive footage of the boys taking over Venice Beach, bowling with Danny Im and encountering a scandalous situation involving the Playboy mansion? This never-before-seen story will show the amazing time that Jinyoung, CNU, Sandeul, Baro, and Gongchan spent in LA!

imdb.plot outline: Mnet America proudly presents "Go!" as part of our Headliner Series where we bring the party to all of the international K-pop loving fans. "Go! Series" is an hour-long documentary that follows the hottest K-pop acts on their journey to the U.S! Watch as we bring you exclusive clips from all of the U.S. tours as well as backstage footage from the artists themselves.
